description: Gets a list of all virtual machine image versions for the specified location, publisher, offer, and SKU.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

tags.description: Specifies the tags that are assigned to the virtual machine. For more information about using tags, see [Using tags to organize your Azure resources](https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/azure-resource-manager/resource-group-using-tags.md).

location.description: The supported Azure location of the resource.

filter.description: The filter to apply on the operation.
